      "acceptanceCriteria": "Mechanistic justification for power-law hemolysis model; comparison against alternative model forms (e.g., strain-based, mechanistic RBC membrane models); model-form uncertainty quantified.",
      "rationale": "Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger model used without formal model-form uncertainty quantification. Literature shows 300% variation in predicted NIH across published model constants."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
