      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative mapping between simulation input parameters and experimental test conditions; equivalency metrics defined and evaluated for all boundary conditions.",
      "rationale": "Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Formal equivalency assessment between CFD boundary conditions and experimental setup not performed. Inlet turbulence intensity assumed 5% in simulation; not measured in experiments."
    }
  ],
